WEBVTT

00:06.441 --> 00:08.138
Previously on
"Just Add Magic"...

00:08.225 --> 00:09.661
I'm telling you,
he took a bite,

00:09.748 --> 00:11.446
and then just disappeared
into thin air.

00:11.533 --> 00:13.317
That wasn't the spell.
It was just supposed to

00:13.404 --> 00:14.623
keep him away
from magic.

00:14.710 --> 00:15.798
We've got to
bring him back.

00:15.885 --> 00:17.669
We will, Gina.
I promise.

00:17.756 --> 00:19.584
If you really wanted
to bring him back,

00:19.671 --> 00:21.021
why didn't you just
use your morbium?

00:21.108 --> 00:24.067
He stole my seed
when he stole Ida's.

00:24.154 --> 00:27.679
I think Grandma
lied to us.

00:27.766 --> 00:30.117
So you don't
remember anything.

00:30.204 --> 00:31.379
It's all a blank.

00:31.466 --> 00:33.990
But his memories
can come back.

00:34.077 --> 00:36.558
And that makes him
a ticking time bomb.

00:38.647 --> 00:41.519
♪♪

00:43.000 --> 00:49.074
